Minsheng Suspends Trading as Board Debates Refinancing Plan

-- B y   M a r c o   L u i
-- 
2011-02-24T12:24:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-24/minsheng-suspends-trading-as-board-debates-refinancing-plan-1-.html
China Minsheng Banking Corp. said
its shares will be suspended in  Hong Kong  and Shanghai tomorrow.  Trading will be halted pending the release of price
sensitive information, the bank said in a statement to the Hong
Kong stock exchange. A Chinese-language statement said the stock
is being suspended pending a board meeting to discuss amendments
to a refinancing plan.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marco Lui in Hong Kong at 
 mlui11@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nerys Avery at 
 navery2@bloomberg.net  